T02D2011:219b-1: shr'i badzra bhee ra ba stu ti /
T02D2011:219b-3: dpal rdo rje 'jigs byed kyi bstod pa /
T02D2011:219b-4: dpal rdo rje 'jigs byed la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2011:219b-5: mi thung sgeg po sprin 'dra'i mdog /'od zer bye ba 'phros pas bzhengs //
T02D2011:219b-6: mtshan ma 'greng ba ma he'i zhal //
T02D2011:219b-7: gnyis med sbyor bas khyod rgyal mdzad //
T02D2011:219b-8: byol song ma lus thams cad kun //
T02D2011:219b-9: bcu drug zhabs kyis thams cad mnan //
T02D2011:219b-10: brkyang bskum zhabs ni brjid par gnas //
T02D2011:219b-11: stobs ldan khyod la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02D2011:219b-12: glang po'i pags pa phyag gnyis 'dzin //
T02D2011:219b-13: g-yas kyi dad po gri gug ste //
T02D2011:219b-14: gnyis pas mtshon rtse gcig pa 'dzin //
T02D2011:219b-15: gsum pa'i phyag gis gtun shing bsnams //
T02D2011:219b-16: bzhi pa chu gri bzang po 'dzin //
T02D2011:219b-17: lnga pa rdo rje rtse gcig bsnams //
T02D2011:219b-18: drug pa'i phyag gis sta re 'dzin //
T02D2011:219b-19: bdun pa'i phyag gis mdung 'dzin te //
T02D2011:219b-20: brgyad pa'i phyag gis mda' 'dzin to //
T02D2011:219b-22: bcu pa khyab 'jug dbyug to bsnams //
T02D2011:219b-23: bcu gcig rtog 'joms kha tv'am ga / chos 'khor bskor ba bcu gnyis pa //
T02D2011:219b-24: bcu gsum ye shes rdo rje 'dzin //
T02D2011:219b-25: bcu bzhi brdungs don thob bsnams //
T02D2011:219b-26: bco lnga dgra gsod ral gri 'dzin //
T02D2011:219b-27: bcu drug cang te'u gnyis med brdung //
T02D2011:219b-29: g-yon gyi dang pos thod pa 'dzin //
T02D2011:219b-30: g-yon gyi gnyis pas tshangs mgo bsnams //
T02D2011:219b-31: gsum pa shes rab phub 'dzin te //
T02D2011:219b-32: bzhi pa bsgrub bya'i rkang pa 'dzin //
T02D2011:219b-33: lnga pa bcing don zhags pa 'dzin //
T02D2011:219b-34: drug pa gzhu 'dzin thabs kyi don //
T02D2011:219b-35: bdun pa nyon mongs rgyu ma 'dzin //
T02D2011:220a-1: dgu pa rdeg don lag pa 'dzin //
T02D2011:220a-2: bcu pa bri don dur khrod ras //
T02D2011:220a-3: bcu gcig gsal shing nyon mongs 'bugs //
T02D2011:220a-4: bcu gnyis sreg don me thab 'dzin //
T02D2011:220a-5: bcu gsum pa na thod tshal 'dzin //
T02D2011:220a-6: bcu bzhi sdigs mdzub bsdigs par mdzod //
T02D2011:220a-8: bsgrub bya rlung bskur bcu drug ras //
T02D2011:220a-10: dur khrod chen po'i dkyil 'khor na //
T02D2011:220a-11: sna tshogs padma nyi ma'i gdan //
T02D2011:220a-12: gzhal yas me dpung dkyil na bzhugs //
T02D2011:220a-14: brgya phyed mgo bo'i do shal can //
T02D2011:220a-15: dbu rgyan thod pa lnga lngas brgyan //
T02D2011:220a-16: dbu skra ser po gyen du 'bar //
T02D2011:220a-17: zhal dgu pa la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D2011:220a-18: spyan bzlog nyi shu rtsa bdun dmar //
T02D2011:220a-19: ljags 'dril zhal nas ha har bshad //
T02D2011:220a-20: mtshan dang dpe byad yang dag ldan//
T02D2011:220a-21: ma he'i zhal la phyag 'tshal bstod //
T02D2011:220a-22: 'di ni bstod pa'i dam pa yin //
T02D2011:220a-23: rnal 'byor kun gyis rnyed dka' ba //
T02D2011:220a-25: don yod rdo rje mkhas pas byas //
T02D2011:220a-26: 'di byas pa yi dge ba yis //
T02D2011:220a-27: kun gyis 'jigs byed zhal mthong shog / dpal rdo
T02D2011:220a-28: rje 'jigs byed kyi bstod pa pandi ta don yod
T02D2011:220a-29: rdo rjes mdzad pa rdzogs so /
